These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, watermelon, cherry, cucumber, cauliflower, cabbage, papaya
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, funk, pop, folk, soul, jazz, blues
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the fan of electronic is the person eating papaya##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 5. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 9. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
10. the person eating cucumber is the fan of funk##1
11. the person eating cucumber is between the fan of pop and the person eating cherry##2
12. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| Food   | cabbage  | cucumber | cherry  | cauliflower | cranberry | watermelon | papaya |
| Music-Genre           | pop | funk   | blues | folk  | jazz   | soul    | electronic    |

