.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, february, june, july, december, august, march
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, amaryllis, daffodil, rose, zinnia, tulip
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
11. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Birthday      | june | july | august   | february | march | september     | december |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | iris  | rose | zinnia     | tulip  | amaryllis | daffodil |

