.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-19::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: lavender, orange, blood-red, aquamarine, green, azure, blue
7 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, hamster, dog, mouse
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the person who likes blue is the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person who likes green is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the hamster and the person who likes blue##2
 9. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
11. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |   7    |
| Color   | orange         | aquamarine | blood-red   | lavender        | blue  | azure  | green |
| Pet         | ferret | frog  | guinea-pig | hedgehog | mouse | dog | hamster |

