.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, water, cola, iced-tea, milk, 7up
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, fuchsia, yellow, ivory, ebony, amber
 1. the person who likes amber is the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes green is between the person who likes ivory and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking milk##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
11. the person who likes green is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Beverage           | cola | mirinda   | iced-tea | water    | lemonade   | 7up | milk     |
| Color   | amber    | aquamarine | yellow        | green | ivory | ebony   | fuchsia |

 